---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import ReviewSummary from '../../components/ReviewSummary.astro';

const testData = {
  platformName: "Test Tutor",
  score: 4.5,
  pros: [
    "Affordable pricing starting at $10",
    "Native speakers available 24/7",
    "Great mobile app for learning on the go",
    "Structured curriculum for beginners"
  ],
  cons: [
    "Limited advanced business courses",
    "Customer support can be slow",
    "Trial lessons are not free"
  ],
  ctaUrl: "https://example.com/go/test-tutor"
};
---

<Base title="Widget Test Page" description="Testing the Review Summary widget implementation.">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Review Summary Widget Test</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p>
        This is a test page to demonstrate the new Review Summary widget. On desktop, the widget should appear on the right and stay sticky as you scroll. On mobile, it should appear right here, at the top of the content.
      </p>

      <ReviewSummary 
        platformName={testData.platformName}
        score={testData.score}
        pros={testData.pros}
        cons={testData.cons}
        ctaUrl={testData.ctaUrl}
      />

      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Section 1: The Basics</h2>
      <p>
        Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.
      </p>
      
      <div style="height: 500px;"></div> <!-- Spacer to test stickiness -->

      <h2>Section 2: Deep Dive</h2>
      <p>
        Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo.
      </p>

      <div style="height: 500px;"></div> <!-- Spacer to test stickiness -->

      <h2>Section 3: Final Thoughts</h2>
      <p>
        Nemo enim ipsam voluptatem quia voluptas sit aspernatur aut odit aut fugit, sed quia consequuntur magni dolores eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Base>
